Milkslop
========

A standalone WebGL2 port of the MilkDrop 2 music visualizer.

This software is a derivative work of MilkDrop 2, and incorporates algorithms,
constants, and shader logic transcribed from the MilkDrop 2 source code, which
was released under the BSD 3-Clause License.

